CONCEPT COMMANDS

The original game's help index listed concept, concept1, and concept2 as
topics for Palladium RPG mechanics (MDC, PPE, ISP, APM, etc.).

Use these topics instead:
  help combat       combat and damage types
  help stats        attributes
  help score        character sheet
  help psionics     ISP and psi powers
  help spells       PPE and magic
  help bionics      cybernetics
  help levels       experience and advancement

SEE ALSO: concept1, concept2, combat, stats
